{"tid":222641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[怒屌]依家啲港孩好撚賤","createTime":"2017-04-29T16:39:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T13:48:48.000Z","uid":31521,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b7da656c4e478653b40273a695cd0045e30fa91","tid":222641,"uid":31521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T16:39:39.000Z","msg":"真人真事 發生喺我條女身上<br />\n話說佢有個讀緊小三嘅表妹今日嚟佢屋企<br />\n一嚟到就趕走坐緊喺梳化嘅主人家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後入左我條女間房<br />\n話想要佢個唇膏<br />\n因為上次我條女拎左佢張紙一齊摺紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我條女梗係唔理佢<br />\n點知條小學雞趁佢唔知偷撚左一粒人地喺泰國買嘅唇膏走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時無大無細 無禮貌屌鳩埋自己阿爺阿嫲<br />\n上人屋企唔尊重下主人家<br />\n扮abc講哂英文 難頂到死 都算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不問自取，是為賊也<br />\n8，9歲人就偷野<br />\n當正自己係公主 無家教<br />\n基本尊重都唔識<br />\n都唔明佢老豆老母點教女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又一個死港女 大個等俾洋腸屌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345c1286fb8941e81670e8cc333b417fa5214b34","tid":222641,"uid":52146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T16:44:30.000Z","msg":"到佢大個D再慢慢教"},{"pid":"cfcf25075d276ac420bb990cb9568af0024fb263","tid":222641,"uid":57490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T16:46:45.000Z","msg":"而家d老母唔係港女就係支那<br />\n佢地西識教咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a74601e36d8c7228b4eac817370ac72b719848","tid":222641,"uid":31521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:47:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到佢大個D再慢慢教</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n調教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" clas